</taxonomicName>
as its basionym.When elaborating the treatment of 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEDFFAEFB7F2863FECEFE67" authority=", De Candolle (1828)" authorityName=", De Candolle" authorityYear="1828" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">
